nts, scholarship amounts, and real stories await you.","name":"Technology and Innovation Scholarships in Turkiye","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/technology-innovation-scholarships-in-turkey/#richSnippet","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/technology-innovation-scholarships-in-turkey/#webpage"},"image":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/technology-and-innovation-scholarships-in-turkiye.webp"},"inLanguage":"en-US","mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/technology-innovation-scholarships-in-turkey/#webpage"}}]}]}', "content_html" = '<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Technology and innovation scholarships</strong> open new doors for international students who want to study in Turkey in 2025. If you are interested in software, artificial intelligence, engineering or entrepreneurship, these scholarship programs offer you not only financial support but also a career platform.</p>


<div class="wp-block-spacer" style="height: 22px;" aria-hidden="true"> </div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" />
<div class="wp-block-spacer" style="height: 22px;" aria-hidden="true"> </div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="why-turkey-new-center-of-technology-and-innovation">Why Turkey? New Center of Technology and Innovation</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-is-the-vision-of-the-national-technology-move">What is the vision of the National Technology Move?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In recent years, Turkey has taken serious steps in the field of technology with a strategy called the <strong>National Technology Move</strong>. The aim of this vision is to increase domestic and national production, direct young people towards technology and increase global competitiveness. The move led to the creation of <strong>technology and innovation scholarships</strong> for thousands of students.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">We can easily say that the T3 Foundation is one of the strongest structures supporting this vision. <a class="" href="https://t3vakfi.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">T3 Foundation&#8217;s website</a> provides detailed information on scholarship programs, events and projects.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="rising-opportunities-for-international-students">Rising opportunities for international students</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">For international students, Turkey is no longer just about affordable education. It also means being a part of the <strong>developing technology ecosystem</strong>. Foreign students studying in Turkey can exhibit their projects at major organizations such as Teknofest, establish startups in technoparks, and find the chance to advance globally with the support of institutions such as T3.</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="technology-and-innovation-scholarships-types-and-scope">Technology and Innovation Scholarships Types and Scope</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="ozdemir-bayraktar-national-technology-scholarship-program">Özdemir Bayraktar National Technology Scholarship Program</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The <strong>Özdemir Bayraktar National Technology Scholarship Program</strong>, offered by the T3 Foundation, aims to reach students from 81 provinces of Turkey. As of 2025, this program will support up to 5,000 students. Monthly scholarship amounts vary according to the student&#8217;s level of education and program category. For example, in the &#8220;Rising Star&#8221; category, scholars can receive up to USD 1,580 per year. The program provides not only financial support but also mentoring, training camps and project development opportunities.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Applications can be received from a wide range of university students to high school students. For more details about the program, you can check<a href="https://roadtostudy.com/erciyes-universitesi-tanitim-kampus-rehberi/"> Erciyes University&#8217;s announcement.</a></p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="turkey-scholarships-technology-and-innovation-focused-programs">Turkey Scholarships&#8217; Technology and Innovation Focused Programs</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">One of the most well-known scholarships for foreign students, <a class="" href="https://arsiv.turkiyeburslari.gov.tr" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Turkey Scholarships</a> has recently updated its programs within the scope of <strong>technology and innovation scholarships</strong>. This system, which accepts scholars in fields such as artificial intelligence, robotic systems, engineering and software, offers applicants many opportunities such as full scholarships, accommodation and health insurance.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The great thing about this scholarship is that it allows you to choose your own university. In other words, you can specialize in technology by applying to one of the institutions such as METU, Boğaziçi or Sabancı University.</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="who-can-apply-and-how-much-support-can-be-received">Who can apply and how much support can be received</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="application-requirements-and-evaluation-process">Application Requirements and Evaluation Process</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Although the requirements for each scholarship are different, in general, for technology and innovation scholarships you need to have the following qualifications:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>To be studying in the fields of STEM (Science, Technology, Engineering, Mathematics)</li>



<li>Have a high grade point average (usually min. 70%)</li>



<li>Participation in project or technology competitions is preferred</li>



<li>Certificate of proficiency in English or Turkish</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Some programs are only for Turkish-medium departments. But comprehensive systems such as the Turkey Scholarships also include English-language departments. Applications are usually received between January and March each year.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="scholarship-amounts-and-duration-2025-current-data">Scholarship Amounts and Duration (2025 Current Data)</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The following table shows the support provided under technology and innovation fellowships in USD:</p>


<figure class="wp-block-table">
<table class="has-fixed-layout" style="height: 261px;" width="854">
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Scholarship Program</th>
<th>Education Level</th>
<th>Monthly Support (USD)</th>
<th>Term</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>Özdemir Bayraktar &#8211; Rising Star</td>
<td>Undergraduate/Graduate</td>
<td>130 USD</td>
<td>9 months</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Turkey Scholarships &#8211; Technology Area</td>
<td>Bachelor&#8217;s Degree</td>
<td>120 USD</td>
<td>12 months</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Turkey Scholarships &#8211; Innovation Research</td>
<td>Master&#8217;s/PhD</td>
<td>150 USD</td>
<td>12 months + accommodation</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</figure>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The financial support for these scholarships may also vary. </p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="turkeys-best-universities-and-programs-in-technology">Turkey&#8217;s Best Universities and Programs in Technology</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="itu-metu-bogazici-and-other-leading-schools">ITU, METU, Bogazici and Other Leading Schools</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you are considering studying in Turkey with <strong>technology and innovation scholarships</strong>, the university you choose is very important. There are some universities in Turkey that stand out in this field:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Istanbul Technical University (ITU):</strong> It houses many innovative departments, from artificial intelligence engineering to space technologies. It also provides active support to R&amp;D projects.</li>



<li><strong>Middle East Technical University (METU):</strong> One of Turkey&#8217;s most prestigious universities for engineering and computer science. Many of its graduates go on to postgraduate studies in Europe and the US or work directly for global companies.</li>



<li><strong>Boğaziçi University:</strong> Known for its software development and entrepreneurship programs, this school is especially ideal for students who want to expand abroad.</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Most of these universities cooperate directly with both the <strong>T3 Foundation</strong> and <strong>Turkey Scholarships</strong> programs. Therefore, if you get a scholarship, your chances of studying in these prestigious institutions are quite high.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="universities-cooperation-and-entrepreneurship-supports">Universities&#8217; Cooperation and Entrepreneurship Supports</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Many universities no longer only provide theoretical knowledge. Incubation centers, technoparks and startup accelerator programs that bring students directly together with the industry also attract great interest. For example, a project developed at ITU ARI Technopolis can receive investment even before graduation.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">This means that with <strong>technology and innovation scholarships</strong>, you will not only study and graduate, but you will also have the chance to start your own startup.</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="hemen-adim-at-future-engineers-and-entrepreneurs-wanted">Hemen Adım At: Future Engineers and Entrepreneurs Wanted!</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you want to take advantage of these opportunities, you should start preparing for the application process now. Here are a few suggestions:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong><a>T3 Foundation Scholarship Program</a></strong> takes applications every year in the fall. Follow the calendar on the website.</li>



<li>Turkey Scholarships, the <a class="" href="https://arsiv.turkiyeburslari.gov.tr" target="_blank" rel="noopener">official application portal</a> has all the details.</li>



<li>Don&#8217;t forget to prepare all your documents in English and/or Turkish.</li>



<li>If you have projects, be sure to include a presentation file or portfolio.</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Technology and innovation scholarships</strong> are waiting for you. Now is the time to act.</p>', "wp_published_at" = '2025-08-05T14:15:25Z', "wp_modified_at" = '2026-03-15T19:22:53Z', "featured_image" = '{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/technology-and-innovation-scholarships-in-turkiye.webp","alt":"Technology and innovation scholarships in Turkiye","title":"technology-and-innovation-scholarships-in-turkiye"}' WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'technology-innovation-scholarships-in-turkey';
