<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="turkeys-best-universities-and-programs-in-technology">Turkey&#8217;s Best Universities and Programs in Technology</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="itu-metu-bogazici-and-other-leading-schools">ITU, METU, Bogazici and Other Leading Schools</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you are considering studying in Turkey with <strong>technology and innovation scholarships</strong>, the university you choose is very important. There are some universities in Turkey that stand out in this field:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Istanbul Technical University (ITU):</strong> It houses many innovative departments, from artificial intelligence engineering to space technologies. It also provides active support to R&amp;D projects.</li>



<li><strong>Middle East Technical University (METU):</strong> One of Turkey&#8217;s most prestigious universities for engineering and computer science. Many of its graduates go on to postgraduate studies in Europe and the US or work directly for global companies.</li>



<li><strong>Boğaziçi University:</strong> Known for its software development and entrepreneurship programs, this school is especially ideal for students who want to expand abroad.</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Most of these universities cooperate directly with both the <strong>T3 Foundation</strong> and <strong>Turkey Scholarships</strong> programs. Therefore, if you get a scholarship, your chances of studying in these prestigious institutions are quite high.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="universities-cooperation-and-entrepreneurship-supports">Universities&#8217; Cooperation and Entrepreneurship Supports</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Many universities no longer only provide theoretical knowledge. Incubation centers, technoparks and startup accelerator programs that bring students directly together with the industry also attract great interest. For example, a project developed at ITU ARI Technopolis can receive investment even before graduation.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">This means that with <strong>technology and innovation scholarships</strong>, you will not only study and graduate, but you will also have the chance to start your own startup.</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="hemen-adim-at-future-engineers-and-entrepreneurs-wanted">Hemen Adım At: Future Engineers and Entrepreneurs Wanted!</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you want to take advantage of these opportunities, you should start preparing for the application process now. Here are a few suggestions:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong><a>T3 Foundation Scholarship Program</a></strong> takes applications every year in the fall. Follow the calendar on the website.</li>



<li>Turkey Scholarships, the <a class="" href="https://arsiv.turkiyeburslari.gov.tr" target="_blank" rel="noopener">official application portal</a> has all the details.</li>



<li>Don&#8217;t forget to prepare all your documents in English and/or Turkish.</li>



<li>If you have projects, be sure to include a presentation file or portfolio.</li>
</ul>



