<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-are-the-conditions-for-kosgeb-young-entrepreneur-support">What Are the Requirements for KOSGEB’s Young Entrepreneur Support?</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">When it comes to entrepreneurship in Turkiye, young people hold a special place. The government sees this group as the employers of the future and offers several advantages to support them. So, what does it take to benefit from these supports?</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Who Can Apply?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">To be eligible for KOSGEB’s young entrepreneur support, applicants must be under the age of 30, must not have previously been a taxpayer (i.e., have not run a business before), and must complete an approved entrepreneurship training course offered by KOSGEB. These trainings are usually delivered online and last a few weeks.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Application Process and Key Considerations</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">After completing the training, you need to register in the KOSGEB database and upload your business plan. If your plan is approved, you may receive initial startup funding (around $260), along with additional support totaling up to approximately $13,000 for various business expenses. However, it&#8217;s important to remember that there will be a follow-up audit process—your expenditures must be documented properly.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Some young entrepreneurs also choose to get consultancy support during this process. If you want to move forward with fewer mistakes, it may be beneficial to explore these services as well.</p>


<div class="wp-block-spacer" style="height: 22px;" aria-hidden="true"> </div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" />
<div class="wp-block-spacer" style="height: 22px;" aria-hidden="true"> </div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="its-time-for-entrepreneurship-in-turkey">It&#8217;s Time for Entrepreneurship in Turkey!</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">I can say this clearly: <strong>Entrepreneurship</strong> in Turkey is more accessible than ever, especially for young people and international students. As long as you know what you want, do your research and make good use of support mechanisms.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you&#8217;re still wondering &#8220;where to start&#8221;, that&#8217;s where <a>Road to Study</a> comes in. We are planning the right steps together for those who want to get an education and start a startup in Turkey.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Now that you have an idea, you are young, and now that you are reading this, you are motivated. So why don&#8217;t you make today a starting point? </p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-08-05T14:16:36Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-15T19:22:52Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/entrepreneurship-and-business-development-support-in-turkiye.webp","alt":"Entrepreneurship and business development supports in Turkiye","title":"entrepreneurship-and-business-development-support-in-turkiye"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'entrepreneurship-supports-in-turkey' );
