o Study in Turkey","publisher":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#person"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"ImageObject","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/academic-publication-and-thesis-support-in-turkey.webp","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/academic-publication-and-thesis-support-in-turkey.webp","width":"2336","height":"1760","caption":"Academic publication and thesis support in Turkey","inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"WebPage","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/academic-publication-support-in-turkiye/#webpage","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/academic-publication-support-in-turkiye/","name":"Academic Publication Support in Turkiye 2025","datePublished":"2025-08-05T17:22:30+03:00","dateModified":"2026-03-15T22:22:50+03:00","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#website"},"primaryImageOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/academic-publication-and-thesis-support-in-turkey.webp"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Person","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/murat/","name":"Murat","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/murat/","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","@id":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9f5b866231ae7aed7a61015846c1f0ab6c5797b065ec200b93c5e9daa87897af?s=96&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g","url":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9f5b866231ae7aed7a61015846c1f0ab6c5797b065ec200b93c5e9daa87897af?s=96&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g","caption":"Murat","inLanguage":"en-US"}},{"@type":"BlogPosting","headline":"Academic Publication Support in Turkiye 2025","keywords":"Academic Publication,Thesis Support","datePublished":"2025-08-05T17:22:30+03:00","dateModified":"2026-03-15T22:22:50+03:00","articleSection":"Scholarships and Funding","author":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/murat/","name":"Murat"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#person"},"description":"Everything you need to know about the academic publishing process and thesis support in Turkey is here. Read now and don&#039;t miss out on applying for support!","name":"Academic Publication Support in Turkiye 2025","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/academic-publication-support-in-turkiye/#richSnippet","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/academic-publication-support-in-turkiye/#webpage"},"image":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/academic-publication-and-thesis-support-in-turkey.webp"},"inLanguage":"en-US","mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/academic-publication-support-in-turkiye/#webpage"}}]}]}', "content_html" = '<p class="wp-block-paragraph">There are serious support mechanisms for both local and international students who want to publish in Turkey. Especially for master&#8217;s and doctoral level researchers, the publication process is not limited to individual efforts. Various incentive programs are offered through universities, government agencies and private foundations.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="tubitaks-scientific-publications-incentive-program-ubyt">TUBITAK&#8217;s Scientific Publications Incentive Program (UBYT)</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><a href="https://cabim.ulakbim.gov.tr/ubyt/ubyt-s-s-s/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">UBYT program</a> is run by TUBITAK to increase academic publication production in Turkey. This program provides approximately <strong>260 USD</strong> per author for articles published in international refereed journals with a Turkish address. If the number of authors is ten or more, this support is given to each author separately.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">UBYT applications are made through TUBITAK ULAKBIM and updated on certain dates each year. This system, which is one of the most recognized examples of academic publication incentives in Turkey, offers a financial motivation especially for new researchers.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="publication-incentive-practices-in-universities">Publication Incentive Practices in Universities</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In Turkey, not only the state but also universities attach importance to academic publications. For example, <a href="https://bap.istanbul.edu.tr/tr/content/proje-turleri/normal-arastirma-projesi-(nap)" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Istanbul University</strong></a> receives support applications for published books and articles through the Scientific Research Projects (BAP) unit. Similarly<a href="https://bau.edu.tr/icerik/17091-bilim-insani-destekleri" target="_blank" rel="noopener">, <strong>Bahçeşehir University (BAU)</strong></a> also provides incentives in areas such as publications, patents and conference participation.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">These in-university supports include both financial assistance and guidance for students in the publication process. Such micro-level support can actually make a big difference in academic publication production in Turkey.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><a><strong><strong>Differences Between Student Visa and Residence Permit in Turkey</strong></strong></a><strong> </strong>In our article, we also discussed the bureaucratic details that affect the academic process.</p>


<div class="wp-block-spacer" style="height: 22px;" aria-hidden="true"> </div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" />
<div class="wp-block-spacer" style="height: 22px;" aria-hidden="true"> </div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="financial-and-academic-support-for-thesis-writing">Financial and Academic Support for Thesis Writing</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The academic publication process in Turkey often starts with thesis work. Therefore, the support provided during the thesis phase increases both quality and motivation.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="tubitak-1001-program-and-other-national-funds">TUBITAK 1001 Program and Other National Funds</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><a href="https://tubitak.gov.tr/tr/destekler/akademik/ulusal-destek-programlari/1001-bilimsel-ve-teknolojik-arastirma-projelerini-destekleme-programi" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TUBITAK 1001 program,</a> is one of the most comprehensive supports for scientific and technological projects. Teams of researchers, consultants and students can benefit from this support to carry out their own projects. The maximum amount of support is <strong>1,580 USD</strong>. The aim of the program is not only to produce results but also to trigger the scientific publication process.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The articles published as a result of such projects have a much more prestigious place in terms of academic publication in Turkey. Consultant and institutional support is actively engaged throughout the publication process.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="graduate-thesis-support-examples-of-marmara-municipalities-union-and-dokuz-eylul">Graduate Thesis Support: Examples of Marmara Municipalities Union and Dokuz Eylul</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><a href="https://www.marmara.gov.tr/tr/lisansustu-tez-destegi-programi-basvurulari-acildi" target="_blank" rel="noopener">The Union of Marmara Municipalities</a> runs an annual program to support graduate theses. The support amount is <strong>1,580 USD</strong> for a PhD and <strong>660 USD</strong> for a master&#8217;s degree. A similar program is offered by <a href="https://fbe.deu.edu.tr/duyurular/2024-doktora-tez-destegi-programi/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Dokuz Eylul University</strong></a>, where the support amount is around <strong>920 USD</strong>.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">These funds can be used for practical needs, such as the translation of research into the field, surveys and materials. This kind of support is very functional for a student who wants to publish an academic publication in Turkey.</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="academic-tools-and-guidance-for-international-students">Academic Tools and Guidance for International Students</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The academic publication process for international students studying in Turkey can seem complicated at first glance. However, many universities facilitate this process with special counseling and guidance systems.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="consultant-incentives-and-refereed-journal-publications">Consultant Incentives and Refereed Journal Publications</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">With the 2024 update, the contribution of the advisor to a publication prepared by a student at the doctorate or specialization level was also included in the scope of support. In Turkey, not only the student but also the advisor can receive support in the production of academic publications. This two-way incentive system further strengthens academic interaction.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Although publishing in peer-reviewed journals can be a difficult process, it is possible to get consultancy support for such publications in Turkey. Especially the publication ethics guidelines of TUBITAK and YOK are guiding in this regard.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="academic-support-systems-integrated-into-thesis-writing-process-in-turkey">Academic Support Systems Integrated into Thesis Writing Process in Turkey</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The BAP (Scientific Research Projects) departments of most universities provide scholarships, equipment and writing support for students to turn their theses into academic publications in Turkey. University libraries, language editing offices and statistical consultancies are also an integral part of this process.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The existence of such systematic structures is an important advantage for international students who want to publish in Turkey. Even bureaucratic processes such as <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/"><strong>Fingerprint and Biometric Data Collection Procedures in Turkey</strong></a> can become part of this academic system.</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="additional-opportunities-with-research-and-scientific-education-activities">Additional Opportunities with Research and Scientific Education Activities</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The academic publication process in Turkey is not limited to articles and theses; scientific training events and conference participation are also important parts of this process. TUBITAK-funded programs in particular offer students the opportunity to network and gain academic visibility.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="tubitak-2237-a-scientific-training-activities-program">TUBITAK 2237-A Scientific Training Activities Program</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">This program funds short-term scholarly events such as seminars, workshops and workshops. At these events, students can receive training on topics such as academic writing techniques, publication ethics and research methodology. Support generally covers accommodation, transportation and material expenses.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The knowledge gained at such events is directly reflected in the preparation of academic publications in Turkey. Because the trainings provided here aim to increase their ability to publish at the international level.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="conference-attendance-and-travel-expense-incentives">Conference Attendance and Travel Expense Incentives</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Universities such as BAU provide both registration fees and travel expenses for students who want to attend academic conferences. With such support, students can present their thesis or article topics in the international arena.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Such events are critical for the academic publication process in Turkey, as most international journals prefer to have a presentation or workshop experience prior to the research. In addition, by adding this experience to their CV, students can make a more solid start to their academic career.</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="doing-research-in-turkey-a-real-career-step">Doing Research in Turkey: A Real Career Step</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Academic publication in Turkey is not limited to university graduates; it can also be a powerful springboard for students aiming for an international career. As long as you have access to the right resources and plan the process.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="why-broadcasting-in-turkey-is-a-big-plus-for-your-career">Why Broadcasting in Turkey is a Big Plus for Your Career?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Publications with Turkish addresses published on international platforms bring academic prestige to students. Moreover, these publications are recognized by European and Asian universities. Therefore, producing academic publications in Turkey is an effective step not only locally but also on a global scale.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Many students think that publishing is only for professors, but this is completely wrong. In Turkey, graduate students are encouraged to actively participate in the publication process. Consultants, research centers and publication coordinators are involved in this process.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="take-the-first-step-dont-miss-support-applications">Take the First Step: Don&#8217;t Miss Support Applications!</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you want to produce academic publications in Turkey, there are dozens of support programs you can apply for today. From TUBITAK to intra-university funding, you can access many resources. However, keep in mind that most applications open during certain periods.</p>



