<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-intellectual-property-means-and-why-it-matters-for-students">What Intellectual Property Means and Why It Matters for Students</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Simply put, &#8220;intellectual property&#8221; is a system that legally owns your intellectual labor. Have you developed a mobile application? Have you thought of a machine design? Or maybe your thesis proposes a solution that will be the first in the sector&#8230; The way to protect all these ideas is to know <strong>patent and intellectual property</strong> rights.</p>



