<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="turk-akademik-sisteminde-basarili-bir-ogrenci-nasil-olur">


<h3 class="wp-block-heading wp-block-paragraph">How to be a successful student in the Turkish academic system?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">It is important in Turkey to be open to working in groups, to participate in extracurricular projects and to communicate well with professors. In addition, being active in research processes is a feature that scholarship committees will look favorably upon. They don&#8217;t only care about your GPA, but also your social skills.</p>


