<p class="wp-block-paragraph">To avoid panicking at the last minute, break down your preparation into small chunks. It&#8217;s not the end of the world if you don&#8217;t win the interview, but it can change your life if you do. That is why it is important to keep that motivation alive before the scholarship interviews in <strong>Turkey</strong>.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-08-06T12:52:04Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-15T19:22:35Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/points-to-consider-when-applying-for-a-scholarship-in-turkiye.webp","alt":"A student filling out a scholarship application form at a desk","title":"points-to-consider-when-applying-for-a-scholarship-in-turkiye"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'scholarship-interviews-in-turkiye' );
