<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="general-expressions-and-empty-sentences">General expressions and empty sentences</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Sentences like &#8220;I love this program&#8221; or &#8220;Turkey is a beautiful country&#8221; are hollow and often used. Such generalizations do not show why you really want this program.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="exaggerated-praise-or-excessive-sincerity">Exaggerated praise or excessive sincerity</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Overly romanticizing about Turkey or writing the letter as if it were an intimate e-mail can also lead to misunderstandings. Balance is very important: you have to keep a warm but academic tone.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">✅ <strong>5 Common Mistakes to Avoid</strong></p>



<ol class="wp-block-list">
<li>Using generic rather than application-specific wording</li>



<li>State your request directly without introducing yourself</li>



<li>Sorting achievements and writing them like a &#8220;google cv&#8221;</li>



<li>Keeping a letter too long (or too short)</li>



<li>Not indicating level of Turkish or cultural interest</li>
</ol>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="extra-tricks-for-turkey-scholarships">Extra Tricks for Turkey Scholarships</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The &#8220;Turkey Scholarships&#8221; program looks not only for academic achievement, but also for contribution to society, leadership potential and cultural fit. That&#8217;s why your motivation letter should be a story, not a resume.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="evaluation-criteria-of-turkey-scholarships">Evaluation criteria of Turkey Scholarships</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The applicant&#8217;s reasons for choosing Turkey, how they will bring their education to their home country and how open they are to cultural adaptation are examined in detail. In other words, you should not say &#8220;I want a scholarship&#8221;, you should say &#8220;I will use this opportunity for my country&#8221;.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading wp-block-paragraph">How should knowledge of Turkish be expressed in a letter?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">It&#8217;s okay that you don&#8217;t speak Turkish. But showing that you are open to learning, perhaps attending <strong>TOMER courses</strong> or checking out resources such as <strong><a href="https://roadtostudy.com/">What you need to know before you start learning Turkish</a></strong> can go a long way. In fact, your interest in Turkish shows your cultural compatibility.</p>



<blockquote class="wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow">
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">You should carefully follow the official guidelines throughout the application process. In particular, you can find up-to-date information about application dates, documents and criteria on the <a class="" href="https://www.turkiyeburslari.gov.tr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Turkey Scholarships official website</a>.</p>
</blockquote>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="example-and-analysis-of-a-real-motivational-letter">Example and Analysis of a Real Motivational Letter</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Analyzing a sample letter is one of the best ways to see what you should and should not do in the writing process. A short excerpt from a sample text is analyzed below.</p>



<blockquote class="wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow">
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">&#8220;Turkey&#8217;s historical and cultural diversity has led me to conduct in-depth research in sociology. Especially the thesis I want to write on Gobeklitepe is an indication of my commitment to this scholarship.&#8221;</p>
</blockquote>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Why is this sentence powerful?</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Certain</strong>: A specific topic such as &#8220;Gobeklitepe&#8221; is specified.</li>



<li><strong>Academic connection</strong>: The field of sociology and the history of Turkey are presented in a connected way.</li>



<li><strong>Abition and a plan for the future</strong>: Clear objectives are mentioned, such as a &#8220;thesis.&#8221;</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">You can create your own letter like this example, with clear goals and personal orientation.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="now-you-can-write-too-take-a-step-to-win-a-turkey-scholarship">Now You Can Write Too: Take a Step to Win a Turkey Scholarship</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Writing a motivational letter for Turkey scholarship should not scare you. Yes, the first sentence is sometimes the hardest to write, but once you start writing, your story will find its own way. Remember: no one expects you to be perfect, just sincere and committed.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Jot down what you&#8217;ve learned in this guide, create an outline, and maybe just write the opening paragraph today. Trust me, taking the first step makes the biggest difference.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">You need help? We are here. You can contact our expert consultants via the <a class="" href="https://roadtostudy.com">Road to Study</a> platform and get sample texts and detailed support.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-08-06T12:58:17Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-15T19:22:34Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/motivation-letter-writing-guide-for-winning-a-scholarship-in-turkiye.webp","alt":"A student writing a motivation letter on a laptop at a study desk","title":"motivation-letter-writing-guide-for-winning-a-scholarship-in-turkiye"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'motivation-letter-for-turkey-scholarship' );
