</ul>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Tell your own story: Answer the question &#8220;Why this scholarship?&#8221; sincerely</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><a href="https://roadtostudy.com/turkiye-akademik-cv-hazirlama/" data-type="post" data-id="2894">How to Prepare an Academic CV for Scholarship Applications in Turkey</a> for a roadmap on the right format and content.</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="to-trust-one-bursa">To Trust One Scholarship</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Applying only to Turkey Scholarships and being disappointed when you don&#8217;t get a result is a non-strategic <strong>scholarship application mistake</strong>. There are many alternative sources in Turkey, from municipalities to foundations. These sources are often less well known and have fewer applicants, which increases the odds of winning.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="alternative-sources">Alternative Sources</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Municipal scholarships</li>



<li>Association and foundation supports</li>



<li>In-college scholarships</li>



<li>Cultural/religious solidarity scholarships</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">You should look for the best scholarship for you, not just the most well-known one. This significantly increases the chances of winning.</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="if-you-dont-apply-now-when">If You Don&#8217;t Apply Now When?</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The habit of procrastination can also be an unseen but serious <strong>scholarship application mistake</strong>. It is always more valuable to take the first step instead of waiting for perfect preparation. Because often the biggest obstacle is not not being ready enough, but not daring to start. To act now is to win tomorrow.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-you-can-do-today">What You Can Do Today?</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Create a scholarship calendar</li>



<li>Check your documents</li>



<li>Assess the application criteria</li>



<li>Get counseling if you need help</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Remember, <strong>scholarship application mistakes</strong> are most common in students who &#8220;never apply&#8221;. If you are reading this, you are already on the right track.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-08-06T14:42:11Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-15T19:22:29Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/the-most-common-scholarship-application-mistakes-in-turkey.webp","alt":"A student looking frustrated while reviewing a rejected scholarship application","title":"the-most-common-scholarship-application-mistakes-in-turkey"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'turkey-scholarship-application-mistakes' );
