</ul>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="alternative-financing-sources-in-turkey">Alternative Financing Sources in Turkey</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">There are many other <strong>student loan</strong> and scholarship options besides the KYK. These include publicly funded scholarships, private funds and bank loans.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="public-scholarships-and-private-funds">Public Scholarships and Private Funds</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><a href="https://ytb.gov.tr/daireler/uluslararasi-ogrenciler" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Turkey Scholarships:</a> Cover accommodation, tuition and monthly living expenses.</li>



<li>TUBITAK: Grants master&#8217;s/doctoral scholarships in research and technology.</li>



<li>Foundation and association scholarships: It is non-refundable and distributed according to very different criteria.</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Many students can benefit from more than one scholarship at the same time. For details, see <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/turkiyede-burs-olanaklari/" data-type="post" data-id="2915">Possibilities to Benefit from Multiple Scholarships in Turkey</a>.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="education-financing-with-bank-loans">Education Financing with Bank Loans</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Especially for international students who are not eligible to apply to KYK, banks can offer low-interest <strong>education loans</strong>. Here are its features:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>12-60 month term</li>



<li>Family coverage may be required</li>



<li>May offer grace period options</li>
</ul>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="step-now-for-the-education-you-dream-of">Step Now for the Education You Dream of!</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Education is a cost, but it is also the best investment. If you want to study at university in Turkey, many different <strong>student loan</strong> and scholarship options are waiting for you.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="reaching-the-right-source-is-easier-than-you-think">Reaching the Right Source is Easier Than You Think</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Everything starts with research. By regularly following resources like Road to Study, you can access not only information but also opportunities.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-08-07T14:04:10Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-15T19:22:22Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/student-loan-opportunities-and-repayment-conditions-in-turkiye.webp","alt":"A student calculating loan repayment on a notebook beside a laptop","title":"student-loan-opportunities-and-repayment-conditions-in-turkiye"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'student-loans-in-turkey' );
