<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="valid-discounts-in-museum-and-culture-areas">Valid Discounts in Museum and Culture Areas</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The most well-known example is the <strong>Museum Card Student</strong>, or Museum Card. The card costs only 1.30 USD and is valid for <strong>one full year</strong>. With the card, you can enter many of Turkey&#8217;s most important museums and archaeological sites for free or at very low prices.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you are interested in cultural events, I suggest you take a look at this article for detailed information: <a class="" href="https://roadtostudy.com">Cultural Events with Student Discount in Turkey</a></p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="student-discount-cards-isic-and-turkish-student-id">Student Discount Cards: ISIC and Turkish Student ID</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">One of the most powerful cards you can get while studying in Turkey: <a href="https://isicturkiye.com/tr/indirimler" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>ISIC &#8211; International Student Identity Card</strong>. </a> This card is a student ID and discount card that is valid not only in Turkey but also worldwide. In Turkey, it offers valid advantages both in cultural activities and in technology and software products.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">ISIC cardholders earn significant profits, especially in the field of educational technology. For example:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Adobe Creative Cloud</strong> software up to 40% off</li>



<li>Membership advantages on online education platforms</li>



<li>Special rates at museums, travel agencies and restaurants</li>
</ul>


<figure class="wp-block-table">
<table class="has-fixed-layout">
<thead>
<tr>
<th>ISIC Benefits</th>
<th>Average Discount Rate</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>Adobe Photoshop, Illustrator, etc.</td>
<td>40%</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Museums and cultural events</td>
<td>30-50%</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Online courses and software licenses</td>
<td>25-60%</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</figure>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you come to Turkey and use your ISIC card actively, you will save a lot of money not only in academic terms but also in your living budget. This is one of the most global and effective options among <strong>student discounts</strong>.</p>


