<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="student-discounts-on-digital-platforms">Student Discounts on Digital Platforms</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Thanks to <strong>student discounts</strong>, you can get serious advantages in digital services that have become an indispensable part of today&#8217;s student life. It is possible to use these apps while studying and relaxing without breaking the bank.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="popular-digital-services-and-discount-details">Popular Digital Services and Discount Details</h4>



<figure class="wp-block-table"><table class="has-fixed-layout"><thead><tr><th><strong>Service</strong></th><th><strong>Note</strong></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Spotify Premium</td><td>Requires verification with SheerID</td></tr><tr><td>YouTube Premium</td><td>Music + ad-free video</td></tr><tr><td>Microsoft 365</td><td>University email required</td></tr><tr><td>Adobe CC (ISIC)</td><td>isicturkiye.com</td></tr><tr><td>Canva Pro</td><td>Education via email</td></tr><tr><td>Notion Plus Plan</td><td>Student email is sufficient</td></tr><tr><td>Figma Education</td><td>Pro features included</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">With most of these services, you just need your university email address (for example <em>@edu.tr</em>) or a student ID to prove that you are a student. Many ask for verification once a year, so don&#8217;t forget to check the calendar.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Thanks to these advantages, digital tools offer powerful support to students in terms of both academic success and social life. Another great thing about being a university student in Turkey is to experience this digital comfort at affordable prices! </p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Student Deals on Food, Clothing, and Entertainment Brands</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Student life isn&#8217;t just about studying, is it? You also need to go out every now and then, grab a bite to eat with friends, or go shopping. Fortunately, student discounts in Turkey don&#8217;t leave you wanting in those areas.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="discount-hunt-with-the-bistudent-app">Discount Hunt with the Bi&#8217;Student App</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Thanks to the mobile application called Bi&#8217;Ogrenci, you can instantly verify your student status and shop with discounts at many brands. From clothing stores to coffee chains, many places offer special discounts. The best part of the app is that the campaigns are constantly updated.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Popular Discounts:</strong></p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Starbucks: Buy 1 get 1 free campaign (on certain days)</li>



<li>10-15% off brands like H&amp;M and Mavi</li>



<li>Special student menus via Yemeksepeti and Getir</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">These types of deals are described in more detail in our article <a class="" href="https://roadtostudy.com">Discount Periods and Deals for Shopping in Turkey</a>.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="cinema-theater-and-fast-food-chains">Cinema, Theater and Fast Food Chains</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Major movie theaters such as Cinemaximum and Paribu Cineverse offer up to 50% advantages in certain sessions as part of <strong>student discounts</strong>. In addition, student menus at restaurants such as McDonald&#8217;s, Burger King and Popeyes are quite affordable.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">These discounts can sometimes be activated by simply showing a student ID and sometimes through applications.</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="advantage-packages-from-mobile-operators-and-banks">Advantage Packages from Mobile Operators and Banks</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">When you come to Turkey, you don&#8217;t have to wait long to get a phone line or open a bank account. Moreover, <strong>student discounts</strong> are also available for these services.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="vodafone-turk-telekom-and-turkcell-student-packages">Vodafone, Turk Telekom and Turkcell Student Packages</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">These three major operators offer low-cost talk and internet packages for students. Especially Vodafone&#8217;s Red Student Package offers advantages in both domestic and international use.</p>


