</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</figure>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="suggestions-for-bank-cards-and-allowance-management">Suggestions for Bank Cards and Allowance Management</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Large banks such as Ziraat Bank and Turkiye İş Bankası offer special debit cards for students. Some cards offer zero transaction fees and sometimes even movie tickets as a gift. Such campaigns are one of the financial advantages that fall under <strong>student discounts</strong>.</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="how-to-apply-for-all-these-benefits">How to Apply for All These Benefits</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">It may sound a bit complicated at first, but the application process for all these <strong>student discounts</strong> is actually quite simple. There are usually 3 main ways:</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="authentication-via-e-government">Authentication via E-Government</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you have received a T.R. ID number after enrolling at university, you can go to the e-Government platform to create a student certificate. This document is sufficient for most advantage programs.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="get-support-from-university-counseling-centers">Get Support from University Counseling Centers</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Some universities (especially public and foundation universities in big cities) have set up information offices in student affairs. There you can get information about your student card, transportation card documents and campaign referrals.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Using these ways, you can benefit from all discount systems. Remember, <strong>student discounts</strong> are a privilege to be actively pursued, not passively.</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="now-is-the-time-to-be-a-student-in-turkey">Now is the time to be a student in Turkey!</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Study in Turkey is advantageous not only in terms of academics but also in terms of living expenses. All the <strong>student discounts</strong> mentioned above allow you to live a comfortable student life without any hardship.</p>



