<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Travel is not limited to the city; there are also special opportunities for students in intercity transportation. For this, you can check out this detailed guide: <a class="" href="https://roadtostudy.com">Student Discounted Transportation in Turkey</a></p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="special-discounts-for-students-on-flight-tickets">Special Discounts for Students on Flight Tickets</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Particularly <strong><a href="https://www.turkishairlines.com/en-int/student/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Turkish Airlines</a></strong> has special programs that offer students up to 20% discount. Additional advantages such as no penalty if you need to change your flight date are also offered. Advantages in flight tickets are generally valid for flights from big cities such as Istanbul and Ankara.</p>



