<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="giant-discounts-in-technology-and-education">Giant Discounts in Technology and Education</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">A laptop for studying, Adobe programs for making videos, or a smartphone just to browse social media&#8230; Opportunities for these technological needs for students in Turkey are really abundant.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="apple-samsung-and-vatan-bilgisayar-campaigns">Apple, Samsung and Vatan Bilgisayar Campaigns</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Apple and Samsung organize special campaigns for education in Turkey. It is usually enough to register with your university e-mail. Local stores like Vatan Bilgisayar have a state-sponsored &#8220;tax-free product&#8221; program. You can buy devices under 250 USD tax-free.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="adobe-creative-cloud-and-digital-education-platforms">Adobe Creative Cloud and Digital Education Platforms</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Adobe offers discounted packages for students, allowing you to use applications such as Photoshop, Illustrator, Premiere Pro at very affordable prices. Some digital education platforms (e.g. Udemy, Coursera) also offer big discounts with a student certificate.</p>


