<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Gaining financial freedom while living in Turkey is entirely in your hands. <strong>Student credit cards</strong>, when used correctly, can help you manage your spending and set you free. But remember, every credit card is a debt instrument. If you act with a plan, the cards don&#8217;t rule you, you rule them.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Now is the time to choose the best student credit card for you and manage your budget wisely. Anyway, if you need help with this, the <a class="" href="https://roadtostudy.com">Road to Study</a> team is always there for you.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-08-07T14:40:03Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-15T19:22:14Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/student-credit-cards-and-financial-management-in-turkiye.webp","alt":"A student holding a credit card while managing finances on a laptop","title":"student-credit-cards-and-financial-management-in-turkiye"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'turkey-student-credit-cards' );
