<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="how-much-is-the-cost-of-living-for-international-students-in-turkey">How Much is the Cost of Living for International Students in Turkey?</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="daily-expenses-in-turkey-average-expenses">Daily Expenses in Turkey: Average Expenses</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In the table below you can see the average monthly expenses of an international student in Turkey. All figures are calculated in USD at the current exchange rate (1 USD = 38 TL).</p>


<figure class="wp-block-table">
<table class="has-fixed-layout">
